<div id="outline-container-sec-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1">About</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<div class="warning">
<p>
This website is under construction
</p>

</div>


<div style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0); border=0px;" class="sidebar">

<div class="figure">
<p><img src="images/TH_small.png" alt="TH_small.png" />
</p>
</div>

</div>
<p>
I am a Senior Lecturer in Pure Mathematics at the
<a href="http://web.am.qub.ac.uk/wp/msrc/">Mathematical Sciences Research Centre</a>, School of Mathematics and Physics,
<a href="https://www.qub.ac.uk/">Queen's University Belfast</a>.
</p>

<hr  />

<p>
<b>Research interest</b>
</p>

<p>
My research interests are in algebra, specifically on graded algebra,
algebraic <i>K</i>-theory and homological finiteness conditions.
</p>

<hr  />

<p>
<b>Administration</b>
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>External examiner for UG Mathematics at Swansea University
</li>
<li>Exams Liaison Officer
</li>
<li>Erasmus Coordinator for Mathematics
</li>
<li>Level-1 coordinator for Mathematics and Statistics
</li>
<li>Computing and publicity officer for MSRC
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

